<paragraph blockId="205.[95,1198,2213,2335]" box="[96,178,2213,2255]" pageId="205" pageNumber="809">
<figureCitation box="[96,178,2213,2255]" captionStart="Plate 52: Muridae" captionStartId="205.[99,129,3295,3316]" captionTargetBox="[12,2735,14,3650]" captionTargetPageId="204" captionText="605. Dalton’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys daltoni), 606. Hartwig’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys hartuig), 607. [MISSING], 608. [MISSING], 610. Tullberg’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys tullbergi), 612. Lukolela Softfurred Mouse (Praomys lukolelae), 613. Least Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys minor), 614. Misonne’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys misonner), 615. Riverine Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys mutoni), 616. Petter’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys petteri), 617. Verschuren’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys verschureni), 619. Delicate Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys delectorum), 620. Coetzee’s Soft-furred Mouse (Praomys coetzeei), 621. Yemen Meadow Mouse (Myomyscus yemeni), 622. Brockman’s Meadow Mouse (Myomyscus brockmani), 623. Angolan Meadow Mouse (Myomyscus angolensis), 624. Verreaux’s Meadow Mouse (Myomyscus verreauxi), 625. Woosnam' ’ s Broad-headed Mouse (Zelotomys woosnami), 626. Hildegarde’s Broad-headed Mouse (Zelotomys hildegardeae), 627. Eurasian Harvest Mouse (Micromys minutus)" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6888311" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6888311/files/figure.png" pageId="205" pageNumber="809">606.</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
